# Cursor Rules for Passport Data Entry Project

## Button Visibility Guidelines
- Always ensure buttons have strong, visible styling with inline styles as fallback
- Use dark backgrounds (bg-blue-600 or darker) with white text for primary buttons
- Add border-2 with darker border color for better visibility
- Include min-width to prevent buttons from being too small
- Use whitespace-nowrap to prevent text wrapping
- Add shadow-lg for depth and visibility
- For search buttons specifically, always include:
  - Inline style with background-color and color
  - Strong border (border-2)
  - Icon or emoji for visual clarity (🔍 for search)
  - min-width to ensure button is always visible

## Search Functionality
- Search buttons must be clearly visible on all pages
- Use consistent styling across dashboard and other pages
- Always include a "Clear" button when search query is active

